Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: One of the best in Amsterdam. Amazing coffee, we tried a flat white, a cappuccino, a latte and all were top notch. The baked goods are also delicious!

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Picked up a bag of espresso earlier this week, also had an espresso whilst in the cafe - both products are excellent, nice ambience and neighbourhood with lots of friendly faces and workers.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Great coffee, nice personnel. Go here for a chat with friends, not suitable for working (they don't provide wifi).

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Sadly, closed with no news on whether they have moved or what. Disappointing.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Amazing coffee, nice service. Go here for the coffee or tea; the cake selection is small.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Great coffee. Unfortunately closed now because they (apparently) did not have the appropriate permits.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Great coffee, good atmosphere and friendly staff. Recommended.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Super good coffee - must try their Ethiopian Espresso

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Great coffee, friendly staff, nice interior...perfect!

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Best for filter and espresso coffee in Amsterdam run by super nice guys!!

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Coffee at its best. Single O's, V60, etc. Cute and friendly little cafe.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Delicious coffee and great service. Bought beans to take home.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Tried a number of the other "best in Amsterdam" roasters. This one is the best in my view.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Super strange working time. It was 3 times when I came here, but it was closed in spite of google & working hours says - it is open.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Yup, these people are top notch. Worth going out of your way.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Hours said open on Friday at 8AM. It was closed at 10:00am on Friday.

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Awesome store, awesome coffee, awesome fresh beans!

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: best specialist coffee roasters in Amsterdam

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Great filter coffee!

Name: Headfirst Coffee roasters
Review Text: Unfortunately the place is closed, check facebook page
